=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains configurations defining enrollment behavior for the batch job.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 ExistingEnrollmentAction => Str

The action to take when the specified speaker is already enrolled in
the specified domain. The default value is C<SKIP>, which skips the
enrollment for the existing speaker. Setting the value to C<OVERWRITE>
replaces the existing voice prints and enrollment audio stored for that
speaker with new data generated from the latest audio.


=head2 FraudDetectionConfig => L<Paws::VoiceID::EnrollmentJobFraudDetectionConfig>

The fraud detection configuration to use for the speaker enrollment
job.



